>h1 HolyC-Style CupidC Features
Verified against source on: 2026-04-10
>style bg #F7F4EC
>style body #1A1A1A
>style h1 #B03060
>style h2 #2B4FA8
>style h3 #9A5A00
>style rule #B8B1A3
>style box #EEE7D8
